text: Nughedu San Nicolò (Nughèdu) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 819 people lived there. Its area is 67.89 km². It is 577 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Nughedu Santa Vittoria
